    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The log file always contains the errors even if they're not emitted to the screen during the test run. I can add functionality to Test-PSPesterResults to emit the errors before throwing. This is probably the best we can hope for because there is so much output there is no way that Travis-CI will be able to run all of our tests.",
